      <description>&lt;p&gt;Functions used to interact with the user in the browser environment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;All these three methods are modal: they pause the script execution and don&amp;rsquo;t allow the visitor to interact with the rest of the page until the window has been dismissed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
